1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:03,400
ALEX REED:
Hello and welcome

2
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:06,000
to The Evening Roundup,
your weekly news review.

3
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:08,600
This week, the Daily Beacon
ran a front-page splash.

4
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:11,400
The headline read:

5
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:14,500
Council caught wasting
millions on a mystery scheme.

6
00:00:14,700 --> 00:00:17,200
Strong stuff. But the
council's own report

7
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:19,800
told a very different story.

8
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:22,400
The Beacon later admitted:

9
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:26,000
We may have overstated
the figures in our report.

10
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:28,600
May have? The whole story

11
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:31,500
rested on a number
that did not exist.

12
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:34,200
Over on Channel Nine,

13
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:36,800
the hosts were just as sure:

14
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:40,200
This is the biggest scandal
the city has ever seen.

15
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:43,000
We asked the Beacon
for a comment.

16
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:45,500
They are yet to respond.

17
00:00:45,700 --> 00:00:48,500
And that is all from us.

18
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:51,500
Until next week,
thanks for watching.
